  #### Recent Changes:

  * Trove Creations Linter: check your Trove Creation for common errors before submitting them (use the Trove Creation panel in the sidebar)
  * reimport Trove blueprints for [Frosted Mini Update](http://forums.trovegame.com/showthread.php?51738-Frosted-Mini-Update!-8-18-2015#post327850)
  * reimport Trove blueprints for [Fat Fish & Flashy FX Edition](http://forums.trovegame.com/showthread.php?47978-Fat-Fish-amp-Flashy-FX-Edition#post306732)
